{"subject": "📊 Daily Portfolio: Markets closed | CAPR AdCom 9 days — FDA briefing docs July 25", "html_body": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Daily Portfolio — July 20, 2026</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f5f7; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #111827;\">\n\n<table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color: #f4f5f7; padding: 24px 12px;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;\">\n\n        <!-- MARKETS CLOSED BANNER -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 10px 24px; background-color: #1e293b; border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;\">&#9899; NYSE CLOSED &mdash; Sunday, July 20, 2026 &mdash; Prices reflect Friday July 18 close (estimated)</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- HERO BANNER -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #334155 100%); padding: 32px 24px; color: #ffffff;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #94a3b8;\">Daily Portfolio Check</p>\n            <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #cbd5e1;\">Sunday, July 20, 2026 &mdash; Kuwait (UTC+3)</p>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Open P&amp;L (Position)</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;$19.68 <span style=\"font-size: 18px; opacity: 0.8;\">(&#8722;6.0%)</span></p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\">&#9888;&#65039; Price approx. $19.12 from search &mdash; all Yahoo Finance API endpoints returned 403. Verify in IBKR.</p>\n                </td>\n                <td align=\"right\" valign=\"bottom\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Friday P&amp;L (est.)</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;$5.12 (&#8722;1.6%)</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n\n            <!-- Investment goal tracker -->\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #475569;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">&#127919; <strong>Investment goal:</strong> $756.15 / $1,000 &mdash; <span style=\"color: #9ca3af; font-weight: 600;\">$243.85 to go</span> (75.6% there)</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 6px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\">Target date: July 31 (11 days). Only path: CAPR AdCom positive (TP1 $35 &rarr; portfolio hits $1,010).</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n\n            <p style=\"margin: 16px 0 0 0; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #475569; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">&#128202; CAPR AdCom in 9 days (Jul 29). FDA briefing docs drop Jul 25 &mdash; that&rsquo;s the read before the vote.</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- MACRO CONTEXT CARD -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 16px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background: #0d0d0d; border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 6px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 14px 18px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #f59e0b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 700;\">&#127758; MACRO CONTEXT &mdash; July 20, 2026</p>\n\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0; width: 50%;\">Buffett Indicator:</td>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;\">\n                        <span style=\"color: #ef4444;\">237.9%</span>\n                        <span style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 1px 7px; background-color: #7f1d1d; color: #fca5a5; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 6px;\">&#128308; ALL-TIME EXTREME</span>\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">S&amp;P Forward P/E:</td>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #fbbf24;\">20.4x <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 400;\">(vs. 10-yr avg 19.0x)</span></td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">Chip Index (PHLX/SOX):</td>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #ef4444;\">&#8722;18.2% for July &mdash; bear market (-20%+ from peak)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">Trend:</td>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 3px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #ef4444;\">&#8593; Rising (was 232.5% June, now 237.9% July)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </table>\n\n                  <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 4px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #e2e8f0;\">Market cap is 2.38&times; the entire US economy &mdash; up from 2.33&times; last month. Every single reading above 190% in history has preceded a multi-year bear market.</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 4px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #fbbf24;\"><strong>For CAPR:</strong> Macro doesn&rsquo;t override your binary catalyst. AdCom outcome is CAPR-specific. But if the AdCom vote is positive and you hit TP1 ($35), take it &mdash; don&rsquo;t hold into a macro headwind waiting for the PDUFA.</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;\">Historical episodes at this level: dot-com peak 2000, COVID bubble 2021. Neither ended softly.</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- POSITION NEWS -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 16px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">&#128240; POSITION NEWS &mdash; July 20, 2026</p>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 14px 16px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #1d4ed8;\">&#128309; CAPR &mdash; Capricor Therapeutics</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151;\"><strong>No material new news this weekend.</strong> AdCom July 29 confirmed. PDUFA Aug 22 confirmed. BLA remains on track (CTGTAC committee, HOPE-3 data: PUL v2.0 p=0.03, LVEF p=0.04, all secondary endpoints met).</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151;\"><strong>10 analysts rate BUY, zero Sell/Hold.</strong> Median PT $50 (+162% from est. close). Roth Capital $43 target.</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; padding: 8px 10px; background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #92400e;\"><strong>&#128203; KEY DATE: July 25 (5 days)</strong> &mdash; FDA releases briefing documents. Read them before the AdCom. If FDA appears skeptical of the 2.4% LVEF improvement: consider cutting before the July 29 vote. If supportive: hold through AdCom and sell the reaction same day at $33&ndash;35. GTC sell already set in IBKR &mdash; confirm it&rsquo;s still live.</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 14px 16px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;\">&#128994; VERA &mdash; Vera Therapeutics</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;\">No material news (position CLOSED Jul 17 at $37.74, SL triggered &mdash; net P&amp;L &#8722;$33.28). Monitoring only for lessons.</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- POSITIONS SNAPSHOT TABLE -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">&#9888;&#65039; MANDATORY &mdash; Positions Snapshot (Friday Jul 18 close, est.)</p>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px;\">\n              <thead>\n                <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Status</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Ticker</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Close&#9888;</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">Day</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">P&amp;L $</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 10px 8px; font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\">P&amp;L %</th>\n                </tr>\n              </thead>\n              <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">\n                    <span style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; background-color: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;\">&#9888;&#65039; WATCH</span>\n                  </td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 600;\">CAPR</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">~$19.12&#9888;</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;1.6%</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;$19.68</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;6.0%</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr style=\"background-color: #f9fafb;\">\n                  <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 12px 8px; font-weight: 700;\">TOTAL</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; color: #6b7280;\">&#8212;</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;1.6%</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; font-weight: 700; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;$19.68</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 12px 8px; text-align: right; font-weight: 700; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;6.0%</td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>\n            <p style=\"margin: 6px 0 0 0; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af;\">&#9888; $19.12 is estimated from search results (Yahoo Finance API returned 403 all sources). Last confirmed: $19.44 Jul 17 close. Open July 18 close unknown. <strong>Verify exact close in IBKR before acting.</strong></p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- POSITION DETAIL CARD -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 16px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">Position Detail</p>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 14px 16px;\">\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td>\n                        <span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;\">CAPR</span>\n                        <span style=\"margin-left: 8px; padding: 2px 8px; background-color: #fef3c7; color: #d97706; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;\">&#9888;&#65039; WATCH</span>\n                        <span style=\"margin-left: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #374151;\">Capricor Therapeutics &mdash; DMD cell therapy</span>\n                      </td>\n                      <td align=\"right\" style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;\">\n                        ~$19.12 <span style=\"color: #dc2626; font-size: 13px;\">&#8722;1.6%&#9888;</span>\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </table>\n\n                  <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;\">16 shares @ $20.35 entry (Jul 15). Stock drifted below entry in broad market weakness but thesis intact &mdash; stop $13.00 is 32% below current. The AdCom (Jul 29) is binary. HOPE-3 met all primary and secondary endpoints. 10/10 analysts Buy. The stock fell after the AdCom announcement ($24 &rarr; $19) on &ldquo;unexpected&rdquo; committee review news &mdash; you bought the dip. Now you wait 9 days.</p>\n\n                  <p style=\"margin: 8px 0 4px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #374151;\"><strong>Commission check:</strong> Gross P&amp;L at TP1 $35: (35&#8722;20.35) &times; 16 = +$234.40. Exit commission $1.00. Net: <span style=\"color: #059669; font-weight: 600;\">+$233.40</span> &#10003; Clears the $1 threshold comfortably.</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #dc2626;\"><strong>Bear case:</strong> CRL/negative vote &rarr; ~$13 (stop). Gross loss: (19.12&#8722;13.00) &times; 16 = +nothing (already in loss). Exit commission $1.00. Net loss on full stop trigger: (13.00&#8722;20.35) &times; 16 = &#8722;$117.60 &#8722; $1 exit = <span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">&#8722;$118.60</span>.</p>\n\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280;\">Stop: <span style=\"color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;\">$13.00</span></td>\n                      <td style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;\">Entry: <span style=\"color: #111827; font-weight: 600;\">$20.35</span></td>\n                      <td style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;\">TP1 (AdCom): <span style=\"color: #059669; font-weight: 600;\">$35.00</span></td>\n                      <td style=\"font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280; text-align: right;\">&#127775; AdCom: <span style=\"color: #111827; font-weight: 600;\">Jul 29</span></td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </table>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- EXIT ALERTS -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 14px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 8px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 12px 16px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #92400e; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&#9888;&#65039; Exit Watch &mdash; CAPR</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #78350f; line-height: 1.5;\">\n                    Position is &#8722;6.0% from entry. Per exit rules: &ldquo;down 3&#8211;7% &rarr; &#9888;&#65039; WATCH, check for thesis-breaking news.&rdquo; No thesis-breaking news found. AdCom 9 days out. <strong>Recommendation: HOLD.</strong><br>\n                    &#128204; Watch July 25 FDA briefing docs. If FDA skeptical of 2.4% LVEF &rarr; consider cutting before AdCom. Otherwise hold to TP1 $35.\n                  </p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- FRIDAY'S MOVERS -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;\">&#128200;&#128201; Friday&rsquo;s Movers &mdash; July 18, 2026</p>\n\n            <!-- Macro Context for the Session -->\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #991b1b;\"><strong>Broad market:</strong> S&amp;P &#8722;0.99% (Jul 17), Nasdaq &#8722;1.50% (Jul 17). Semiconductor index (PHLX/SOX) down <strong>1.6% on Friday</strong> &mdash; making it <strong>&#8722;18.2% for July</strong>. The $3.3 trillion chip sell-off hit bear market territory (&#8722;20%+ from June peak of 14,655). Micron down 26.5% for July alone (but +197% YTD). This is a sector rotation out of AI-semis, not a macro collapse.</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n\n            <!-- Specific Movers -->\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;\">&#128200; Top Gainers &mdash; July 18, 2026 (single-session &#8805;20% threshold)</p>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n              <thead>\n                <tr style=\"background-color: #f0fdf4;\">\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; border-bottom: 1px solid #bbf7d0;\">Ticker</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; border-bottom: 1px solid #bbf7d0;\">+%</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; border-bottom: 1px solid #bbf7d0;\">Catalyst</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; border-bottom: 1px solid #bbf7d0;\">Type</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; border-bottom: 1px solid #bbf7d0;\">In play?</th>\n                </tr>\n              </thead>\n              <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 600;\">FDMT</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #059669; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">~+N/A</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">4D-150 Phase 2b AMD data: 78&#8211;87% treatment burden reduction, positive 2yr readout</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">Phase 2b data</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 1px 6px; background-color: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;\">&#10003; WATCH</span></td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>\n\n            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;\">&#9888; Specific small-cap &#8805;20% single-session gainers for Jul 18 could not be confirmed from search results. July monthly top gainers: CRNX +116% (Vertex M&amp;A $85/share &#8212; done), FBRX +103% (vitiligo Phase 1b data Jul 9&#8211;10 &#8212; move complete), TRAX +85% (catalyst unconfirmed). These are monthly moves, not single-session.</p>\n\n            <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 6px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;\">&#128201; Top Losers &mdash; July 18, 2026 (sector-level)</p>\n\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n              <thead>\n                <tr style=\"background-color: #fef2f2;\">\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b; border-bottom: 1px solid #fecaca;\">Ticker/Index</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: right; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b; border-bottom: 1px solid #fecaca;\">&#8722;%</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b; border-bottom: 1px solid #fecaca;\">Catalyst</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 8px 6px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b; border-bottom: 1px solid #fecaca;\">Contagion to portfolio?</th>\n                </tr>\n              </thead>\n              <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 600;\">SOX (PHLX)</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\">&#8722;1.6%</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\">AI capex ROI reassessment, earnings season rotation, Micron -26.5% July</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; color: #6b7280;\">None direct &#8212; CAPR is biotech, not semis</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6; font-weight: 600;\">MU (Micron)</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 8px 6