e when the catalyst scanner surfaces qualified plays. See Catalyst Plays section below for next candidates.</p>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- CATALYST PLAYS -->\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding: 20px 24px 0 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background: #0f1117; border-left: 3px solid #6366f1; border-radius: 8px;\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"padding: 16px 18px;\">\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #818cf8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">&#128225; Catalyst Plays &mdash; July 20, 2026</p>\n                  <p style=\"margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.5;\">&#128270; <strong>30-search scan complete.</strong> Major July PDUFA slate has largely fired: INSM brensocatib (approved Aug 2025), TVTX Filspari FSGS (approved Apr 2026), CELC REVTORPYK (approved Jul 14), VRDN Lumvoa (approved Jun 30), VERA TRUTAKNA (approved Jul 7). Remaining confirmed events with small-cap (&lt;$2B cap) + halal + &#8804;45 days: limited. See analysis below.</p>\n\n                  <!-- Candidate 1: FDMT -->\n                  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border: 1px solid #312e81; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px;\">\n                    <tr>\n                      <td style=\"padding: 12px 14px;\">\n                        <p style=\"margin: 0 0 4px 0;\">\n                          <span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #e0e7ff;\">&#128300; FDMT &mdash; 4D Molecular Therapeutics</span>\n                          <span style=\"margin-left: 8px; padding: 1px 7px; background-color: #1e1b4b; color: #a5b4fc; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;\">BIOTECH / GENE THERAPY</spa